---
title: Chinese Chicken & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: With a luscious, mild oyster and garlic-spiked sauce and a smattering of roasted peanuts to finish the dish, this colourful meal has all the delicious flavours of takeaway, except that it's so much better!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chinese-chicken-stir-fry-b1163bf0.jpg
